[SPEAKER_01] Sad je to samo bol u guzi.

240
00:22:30,960 --> 00:22:32,079
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, doći ćemo do toga.

241
00:22:32,240 --> 00:22:32,720
[SPEAKER_01] Doći ćemo do toga.

242
